text: "Elderly Woman Behind the Counter in a Small Town" is a 1993 song by alternative rock band Pearl Jam and is the tenth track from their second studio album Vs. and was later included in their greatest hits album rearviewmirror (Greatest Hits 1981-1993). == References == Category:1993 songs Category:Rock songs Category:Pearl Jam songs Category:Acoustic rock songs
title: Elderly Woman Behind the Counter in a Small Town
